"28:82:21" : {s: 28, a: 82, w: 21, r: "خسف", t: "لَخَسَفَ", l: "خَسَفَ", lc: 8, tl: "lakhasafa", lb: "ডুবে যাওয়া, ধসে যাওয়া",e: "He would have caused it to swallow us", b: "", i: "tentu Dia telah membenamkan", f: 1, rm: "To sink or go away into the ground or earth (place or person), become depressed (such as the eye becoming depressed in the head), to lose sight/become blind, to lose light (like the sun or moon during an eclipse), become defective or deficient, become lean or emaciated, to recover (such as from disease or illness), to put out ones eye, make a hole in a thing, to abase or humble or make lowly, to disgrace, to be vile.", ag: "لام التوكيد وفعل ماض ", eg: "Emphatic lām and Verb Perfect ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "", deg: "3", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: ""},
